The paper deals with the evaluation of queries over probabilistic databases, which is a topic in the field of databases (cs.DB). The use of decision diagrams and circuit treewidth is a common technique in knowledge compilation, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the tractability of probability computation, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The use of decision diagrams and circuit treewidth is also related to the study of graph algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and circuit complexity (cs.CC).
